c3a05bf0-4394-4803-bed4-ace61268ef25.title: Magic Instructor
c3a05bf0-4394-4803-bed4-ace61268ef25.text:
Good day, newcomer. My name is Terrova. I'm here
to tell you about Magic. Let's start by opening your
spell list. To do this right click your staff.

158b84c3-079d-483d-9126-02310ad2c036.title: Magic Instructor
158b84c3-079d-483d-9126-02310ad2c036.text:
Currently you can only cast one offensive spell called
Wind Strike. Let's try it out on one of those chickens.

args: &rYou need 3 inventory slots free to continue, hover over an item and press "q".
&aEquip your staff by shift clicking in inventory.

8401a468-7bf0-4fab-babe-eb2ec2ddcfed.title: Magic Instructor
8401a468-7bf0-4fab-babe-eb2ec2ddcfed.text:
Well, you're all finished here now. I'll give you a
reasonable number of runes when you leave.
